<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦١٧٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4195">عُبَيْدِ اللهِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span>،<span class="c5"> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«الْغَادِرُ يُرْفَعُ لَهُ لِوَاءٌ يَوْمَ الْقِيَامَةِ،<span class="c5"> يُقَالُ:</span> هَذِهِ غَدْرَةُ فُلَانِ بْنِ فُلَانٍ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>